## VS Code Extensions

- ES7+ React Snippets
- Tailwind CSS IntelliSense
- Prettier
- Auto Rename Tag
- Error Lens

---

## Best Practices

- Break UI into small, reusable components
- Keep `src/components/` organized by feature
- Never commit `node_modules/` ‚Äî it's in `.gitignore` by default
- Push to GitHub regularly